s to people who do not believe in the following verse, }{\b\f0\insrsid16267234\charrsid16267234 "The desert Arabs say, 'We believe.' Say: 'You do not believe. Say rather, 'We have become Muslim,' for faith has not yet entered into your hearts'..." }{
