\par }{\f0\expnd-1\expndtw-5\insrsid16267234\charrsid16267234 If We wished, We would show them to you and you would know them by their mark and know them by the burden of their speech. Allah knows your actions. (Surah Muhammad: 30)}{
\f0\insrsid16267234\charrsid16267234 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qj \fi567\li0\ri170\sl-320\slmult0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin170\lin0\itap0\pararsid16267234 \f8\fs22\lang1024\langfe1024\cgrid\noproof\langnp1055\langfenp1033 {\f0\insrsid2565081 
\par }{\f0\insrsid16267234\charrsid16267234 The defects in these people's speech manifest themselves in a number of ways. The most common ones include: 
\par  
\par }\pard\plain \s21\qj \fi567\li0\ri170\sl-320\slmult0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin170\lin0\itap0\pararsid16267234 \b\f8\fs22\ul\lang1024\langfe1024\cgrid\noproof\langnp1055\langfenp1033 {\f0\insrsid16267234\charrsid16267234 
