\par }\pard\plain \s20\qj \fi567\li0\ri170\sl-320\slmult0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin170\lin0\itap0\pararsid16267234 \f8\fs22\lang1024\langfe1024\cgrid\noproof\langnp1055\langfenp1033 {\f0\insrsid16267234\charrsid16267234 
Some exhibit serious defects in their chain of logic. Most of the time, they themselves are not aware of this collapse of logic, which is readily apparent to others. For example, while trying to p
rove that criticism directed at them is groundless, they put forth evidence to prove that it is incorrect. Every statement they make is based on more twisted logic than before. In every attempt to turn the situation in their favor, they become even more i
rrational.
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s21\qj \fi567\li0\ri170\sl-320\slmult0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin170\lin0\itap0\pararsid16267234 \b\f8\fs22\ul\lang1024\langfe1024\cgrid\noproof\langnp1055\langfenp1033 {\f0\insrsid2565081 \page }{
